---
id: finding-explain-v1
version: 1.0.0
type: context
description: Context template for a single finding explanation
changed: 2026-07-02
---

## Finding
- ID: {{finding.id}}
- Title: {{finding.title}}
- Severity: {{severity-label finding.severity.level}} ({{format-score finding.severity.score}}/10)
- Confidence: {{format-confidence finding.confidence}}
- Rule: {{finding.ruleId}}
- Description: {{finding.description}}

{{#if finding.taxonomyIds}}
- Taxonomy: {{finding.taxonomyIds}}
{{/if}}

## Evidence ({{pluralize evidence.length "match"}})
{{#each evidence}}
### Match {{@index}}{{#if this.id}} ({{this.id}}){{/if}}
- Location: {{this.sourceLocation.path}}:{{this.sourceLocation.startLine}}
- Match type: {{this.matchDetail.kind}}
- Confidence: {{format-confidence this.confidence}}
{{#if this.sourceLocation.snippet}}
- Snippet: `{{this.sourceLocation.snippet}}`
{{/if}}
{{/each}}

{{#if rule}}
## Rule
- ID: {{rule.id}}
- Name: {{rule.name}}
- Description: {{rule.description}}
- Severity: {{severity-label rule.severity.level}} ({{format-score rule.severity.score}}/10)
{{#if rule.packId}}- Pack: {{rule.packId}}{{/if}}
{{#if rule.cweIds}}- CWE: {{rule.cweIds}}{{/if}}
{{#if rule.remediation}}- Remediation: {{rule.remediation}}{{/if}}
{{/if}}

{{#if artifact}}
## Artifact
- Path: {{artifact.path}}
- Type: {{artifact.type}}{{#if artifact.subType}}/{{artifact.subType}}{{/if}}
{{/if}}

{{#if risk}}
## Risk Context
- Risk level: {{risk.overallLevel}}
- Overall risk score: {{format-score risk.overallScore}}/10
{{#if risk.dimensions}}
- Dimensions: {{risk.dimensions.length}}
{{/if}}
{{/if}}
